@startuml SD-08
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11

title SD-08: Manajemen Data Ruangan & Sinkronisasi AI

actor "Admin\n(Browser)" as Admin #4A90D9
participant "Laravel\n(DataRuanganController)" as Controller #2E8B57
participant "DataRuanganService" as RService #50C878
participant "ChatbotService" as CService #27AE60
database "MySQL\n(Database)" as DB #3498DB
participant "Flask\n(app.py)" as Flask #E67E22
participant "ChatbotTrainer\n(trainer.py)" as Trainer #9B59B6

== 1. Admin Tambah Ruangan Baru ==
Admin -> Controller : POST /data-ruangan\n{nama_ruangan: "Poli Gigi", nama_gedung: "Gedung A",\nkata_kunci: "gigi,dental,mulut", foto: [file1, file2]}
activate Controller

Controller -> RService : storeData(validated, files)
activate RService

== 2. Simpan Data Ruangan ==
RService -> DB : INSERT INTO data_ruangans\n(nama_ruangan, nama_gedung, kata_kunci,...)
activate DB
DB --> RService : DataRuangan(id=86) tersimpan
deactivate DB

== 3. Upload Foto Ruangan ==
RService -> RService : Sanitasi nama file\nmenjadi "1718901234_file1.jpg"
RService -> DB : INSERT INTO foto_ruangans\n(path_foto, data_ruangan_id)
activate DB
DB --> RService : foto tersimpan
deactivate DB

RService --> Controller : ruangan + fotoRuangans
deactivate RService

== 4. Jadwalkan Sinkronisasi (Zero-Sync) ==
Controller -> CService : scheduleSync()
activate CService
note right of CService
  Cache::put('chatbot_sync_pending', true)
  Sync ditunda sampai predict() berikutnya
  (Zero-Sync: tidak blokir response)
end note
CService --> Controller : OK
deactivate CService

Controller --> Admin : JSON {message: "Ruangan berhasil dibuat",\ndata: {id:86, ...}}
deactivate Controller

== 5. Sinkronisasi Otomatis (Saat User Chat Berikutnya) ==
Admin -> Controller : POST /chat\n{message: "..."}\n(user berikutnya)
activate Controller #LightBlue
note over Controller
  ChatbotService.predict() dipanggil
  Cek: chatbot_sync_pending = true?
  Ya! Trigger syncModels()
end note

Controller -> CService : syncModels()
activate CService

== 6. Kirim Data ke Flask untuk Retraining ==
CService -> DB : Ambil SEMUA DataRuangan\n+ ChatbotFeedback (yang benar)
activate DB
DB --> CService : rooms[] + feedbacks[]
deactivate DB

CService -> Flask : POST /sync\n{rooms: [86 ruangan],\nfeedbacks: [156 feedback],\nintent_feedbacks: [...]}
activate Flask

== 7. Retraining Model AI ==
Flask -> Trainer : train_rooms(86 rooms, feedbacks)
activate Trainer
note right of Trainer
  Encode 86 ruangan dengan S-BERT
  Buat embedding baru
  Simpan modelDataRuangan.pkl
end note
Trainer --> Flask : rooms_ok = true
deactivate Trainer

Flask -> Trainer : train_intent(intent_feedbacks)
activate Trainer
note right of Trainer
  Latih ulang SVM classifier
  Simpan modelLabel.pkl
end note
Trainer --> Flask : intent_ok = true
deactivate Trainer

Flask -> Flask : svc.reload()\n(muat model baru)
Flask --> CService : {success: true}
deactivate Flask

CService -> CService : Cache::put('last_sync_time', now())
CService --> Controller : sync berhasil
deactivate CService

Controller --> Admin : JSON {message, rooms, intent}
deactivate Controller

note over Admin
  Chatbot sekarang mengenali:
  "Poli Gigi" dengan kata kunci baru
  Model AI sudah diperbarui otomatis
end note

@enduml
